Data Structures 
1. Book Structure 
typedef struct { 
int id;                
char title[100]; 
char author[100]; 
char publisher[100]; 
int quantity;          
} Book; 
Stores information about each book: 
id → Unique identifier 
title, author, publisher → Text info 
quantity → Number of available copies 
2. Issue Structure 
typedef struct { 
int book_id;                  
char student_name[100]; 
char issue_date[20];          
} Issue; 
Tracks issued books: 
Which book ID was issued 
To which student 
On what date 
