Search by Title 
Search books by name or partial text. 
Modify Book Edit book details (title, author, publisher, quantity). 
Delete Book Remove a book permanently from the file. 
Issue Book Issue a book to a student and reduce its quantity. 
Return Book Return a book, increase its quantity, and remove issue record. 
